Title: Association of lifestyle with valvular heart disease progression and life expectancy among elderly people from different socioeconomic backgrounds
Journal: BMC Med
Volume: 22
Issue: 1
Pages: 367
Epub Date: 20240905
Date: Sep 5
Short Title: Association of lifestyle with valvular heart disease progression and life expectancy among elderly people from different socioeconomic backgrounds
ISSN: 1741-7015 (Electronic)
1741-7015 (Linking)
DOI: 10.1186/s12916-024-03576-9
Legal Note: The authors declare no competing interests.
PMCID: PMC11378404
Accession Number: 39237933
