Title: The Potential Psychological Mechanism of Subjective Well-Being in Migrant Workers: A Structural Equation Models Analysis
Journal: Int J Environ Res Public Health
Volume: 16
Issue: 12
Epub Date: 20190624
Date: Jun 24
Short Title: The Potential Psychological Mechanism of Subjective Well-Being in Migrant Workers: A Structural Equation Models Analysis
ISSN: 1660-4601 (Electronic)
1661-7827 (Print)
1660-4601 (Linking)
DOI: 10.3390/ijerph16122229
Legal Note: The authors declare no conflict of interest.
PMCID: PMC6617093
Accession Number: 31238592
Keywords: Adolescent
Adult
China
Depression
Female
